Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:58.05,RomajiOP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,150)}karamaru utsukushi kumo no ito no you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:02.56,RomajiOP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,150)}ugokenai no watashi wo yurushite
