Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:14.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(220,0,200,0,237,237,4157)\c&HC4A0B0&\fscx90\fscy90\pos(1104,77)}kdykoliv
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:14.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(220,0,160,0,237,237,3407)\c&H410A0F&\fscx90\fscy90\pos(197,61)}vynořím se jiná
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(220,0,100,0,237,237,2777)\pos(796,100)\c&H410A0F&\fscx90\fscy90\}závazné\Nprokletí
